<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-55f8ebc805e65b5b71ddafdae390e3be2bcd69af">Description</h2>
This module is exactly ToME but without quests, wilderness multiple towns/dungeons. One town, one dungeon, kill Sauron &amp; Morgoth. <p>
This module serves as both an example and for people who dont want quests and wilderness. 
</p>
<h2 id="head-a69ab6442fa5e4ed9de9974074737205958697f1">Module Version</h2>
1.0.1 <h2 id="head-c0975d85796fcb5ef3b4bf9d9c2388a4b1dc8123">T-Engine version</h2>
2.2.* <h2 id="head-5fda23d62015b99fb2a9f86b38bcdf2bdf7609c8">Author</h2>
<a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20041020135603/mailto:darkgod@t-o-m-e.net">darkgod@t-o-m-e.net</a> <h2 id="head-cf1b91677c424704e7d3a429fb90869242e87885">Last update</h2>
18/12/2003 <h2 id="head-a479c9c34e878d07b4d67a73a48f432ad7dc53c8">Download</h2>
You can download this module as a <a class="external" href=".modules.t-o-m-e.net/mods/1__scroll.tgz"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-www.png" alt="[WWW]" height="11" width="11">tgz file</a>. <p>
